summary: A report detailing the contact with Juanita Reyes, a possible character reference for Manuel Marti; Reyes stated she did not know Marti.
summary_one_paragraph: On November 21, 1968, a report was created documenting the contact with Juanita Reyes of New York, a possible character reference for Manuel Marti. On November 3, 1968, Reyes was contacted telephonically regarding a letter left at her residence on November 1, 1968. Reyes stated she did not recall Manuel Marti and was waiting to consult with her family. After receiving a description of Marti, Reyes stated she was not acquainted with him.
